‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á API Request: EmailService ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á HTTP POST Request ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏¥‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà API ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Mailersend (https://api.mailersend.com/v1/email)
‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏ö Payload: Request Body ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà Mailersend ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏î:
{
  "from": { "email": "booking@yourhotel.com", "name": "Your Hotel Name" },
  "to": [
    { "email": "customer_email@example.com", "name": "Customer Name" }
